            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural and enriched (8.1+/0.2% in 164Er, 33.10+/-3.4%",
                " in 166Er) sample prepared by vacuum evaporation of",
                " Er2O3 powder (114-238 ug/cm2) onto Al backing (2 um).",
